<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Anton');
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans');
        body {
        background-color: #222;
        font-family: 'Anton',  sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        }


        body > main > center > p {
        color: #ddd;
        font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif !important;
        }

        body > main > center > h1 {
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #0077ff;
        font-size: 48px;
        }

        body > main > center > h3 > a {
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #000;
        background-color: #0077ff;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 1px 5px;
        border: 1px solid #0077ff;
        border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
    <title>404 Page Not Found</title>
</head>
<body>

    <main>
      <center>
        <br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br/>
  			<h1>404 - Page not found!</h1>
  			<p>Oops! It seems like you're lost, let me help you find your way back home!<br />
                  The following problems could be the case:<br><br>
                  • The link is broken<br />
                  • This page never existed<br />
                  • This page has been removed<br /><br /><br /></p>
        <h3><a href="/">Click here to go back home</a></h3>
        <br /><br /><br /><br />
      </center>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
